query:
SELECT DISTINCT
                timelines.id AS "id: OpenTimelineId",
                timelines.name AS "name: Name"
            FROM timelines
            JOIN timeline_tags ON timelines.id = timeline_tags.timeline_id
            WHERE
            (
                timeline_tags.name = ?
                OR (timeline_tags.name IS NULL AND ? IS NULL)
            )
            AND timeline_tags.value = ?
